{
  "stem": "6719.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh, I found a gold coin in the, uh, wagon, you know, in the cars, the-- the-- the-- transport, the cattle cars where people were in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I looked at it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And to us this was something that one could use in the camp-- I will tell you later-- because there were favors to be asked for if something happened to you, you needed somebody that you could turn to if-- and it happened to me.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It happened to many of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we gave it to them when we came back, because we didn't use it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't need it in the Kanadakommando, as such.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I pocketed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- you know, it was, it was like the cat watching the mouse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was just waiting-- what I'm going to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I kept it there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He gave me such a beating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, he didn't kill me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He didn't maim me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But he gave me a beating that I felt for a long time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was Hans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this is a lesson to you, he said in Viennese.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SPEAKING VIENNESE] If you do that one more-- one more time, I'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Apparently, I found out, in 1944 this same Hans that behaved sometimes like an animal, that hit me very badly-- I have no scars from it, but very badly-- saved my life.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He found out that I was in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He bribed somebody on there, and they substituted my number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He crossed my number off, said I died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I just got out, that's all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here I can say it's my grandfather, but it's also Hans Schorr.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
